{"tid":38931,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"港女都係諗住搵現貨","createTime":"2016-12-14T08:54:15.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-14T14:57:09.000Z","uid":29934,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"34e9969ca4b6d54e65dbc689a4cb2c619ebca139","tid":38931,"uid":29934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:54:15.000Z","msg":"畢業以來 身邊既女性雖然唔介意出街食飯睇戲<br />\n<br />\n但係識落一排就會發現佢地只係想搵個有車有樓<br />\n<br />\n現成既男人幫佢地埋單<br />\n<br />\n直情有個女仔同我講 佢而家同我捱 第日唔係佢享受成果點算<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係香港 廿幾歲既男仔追女仔個成本真係太大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71cb41e160d0207f7deaee02d1562e7de1ede1b3","tid":38931,"uid":6745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T08:57:28.000Z","msg":"雞黎嘛，正常"},{"pid":"58eb319003672e125abad317178455e3c250a45c","tid":38931,"uid":59038,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:01:46.000Z","msg":"拎碌砲征服佢"},{"pid":"66069829b9b4ca982f185b2a3a7a7e07bc9ef76c","tid":38931,"uid":18363,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:04:35.000Z","msg":"邊個上心邊個死"},{"pid":"7a919cdbea120e826a1e14d5f1bdf38163094a21","tid":38931,"uid":63978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:10:54.000Z","msg":"佢地以為佢地陪你涯<br />\n其實咪又係得你涯緊<br />\n自己一個更開心，洗少份又儲多啲<br />\n過多幾年你咪係現貨囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ec1526bce161e8c48e7ec8d13bb3242f3bf7ea0","tid":38931,"uid":63978,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:13:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>佢地以為佢地陪你涯<br />\n其實咪又係得你涯緊<br />\n自己一個更開心，洗少份又儲多啲<br />\n過多幾年你咪係現貨囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n到時選擇權係邊個度，唔洗我講<br />\n千祈唔好咁快畀人食住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef1c9261bb3abe1b54b386dc13e2e8d558dbc7ac","tid":38931,"uid":63919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:14:55.000Z","msg":"有錢就有女<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/21.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f53f73166c8055a8e949c3279ba2c3fe6eb8eb29","tid":38931,"uid":29934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:20:58.000Z","msg":"有無現貨巴打分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5f4467e807f1e5c4e5e4222a698933d360fbfa4","tid":38931,"uid":7371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T09:32:30.000Z","msg":"女人後生時要靚仔要安全感<br />\n到老D個個都係要錢<br />\n至少身邊見既女性長輩十個有九個都係貪錢<br />\n<br />\n男人幾多歲都係要性<br />\n但女人老得好快<br />\n所以當你身邊個女人越黎越老時<br />\n你自然無和諧性生活同想出軌<br />\n<br />\n大劉有錢玩左好多年女人<br />\n乜野大美人都玩過<br />\n最後先搵到個甘比係較為有情有義<br />\n這就是現實"},{"pid":"b5477cfeb572c7dd5eafb5273885a34a9cf5c96f","tid":38931,"uid":29934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:44:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>女人後生時要靚仔要安全感<br />\n到老D個個都係要錢<br />\n至少身邊見既女性長輩十個有九個都係貪錢<br />\n<br />\n男人幾多歲都係要性<br />\n但女人老得好快<br />\n所以當你身邊個女人越黎越老時<br />\n你自然無和諧性生活同想出軌<br />\n<br />\n大劉有錢玩左好多年女人<br />\n乜野大美人都玩過<br />\n最後先搵到個甘比係較為有情有義<br />\n這就是現實</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"744f058f01783c231f3e3333036c480f9c182a98","tid":38931,"uid":61077,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:47:34.000Z","msg":"比啲心機<br />\n過多幾年<br />\n<br />\n約番呢啲女出黎食飯<br />\n無拖拍既咪approach下<br />\n<br />\n到手再同佢講<br />\n<br />\n我都係唔係好鍾意現貨<br />\n<br />\n純FF"},{"pid":"8b105b5a5b01acc648418d4c491c96b2baa9b0e5","tid":38931,"uid":17792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T10:53:01.000Z","msg":"我識好多女都捱緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪巴打要求太高咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82f0