islike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T12:52:16.000Z","msg":"最緊要留錢 屌你有人月月清仲碌埋卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56b57d97a71153743ef01f2bab3394ad958ea515","tid":38931,"uid":29934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T13:00:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>最緊要留錢 屌你有人月月清仲碌埋卡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n條女拍拍籮友走個時留低既有一頂帽同堆卡數<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a164bc73ef82723389b9ac649e3453a3a9ed78e6","tid":38931,"uid":38954,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-14T14:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>我識好多女都捱緊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係咪巴打要求太高咋<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n搵唔到好碼頭炸？<br />\n我ex初初又話同我捱<br />\n最後咪又係跟左個有錢佬走</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本來有得做少奶奶 但我唔要<br />\n搵番要我捱既初戀 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n辛苦時都有點後悔 但既然選擇咗 唯有努力啲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}